query.result:
58 The world is indeed so entirely deserted
59 of every virtue, as you tell me,
60 and pregnant and covered with malice;

61 but I pray that you indicate to me the cause,
62 so that I see it and show it to others;
63 because in heaven one, and one places it down here.”

82 Therefore, if the present world goes astray,
